{"tid":320141,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求教  部電腦無啦啦開唔到","createTime":"2017-07-13T10:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T12:49:24.000Z","uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f73213062bca66c02a3fe19932181565e8f93afc","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去完個旅行返黎就開唔到機，開主機有咇聲但係畫面冇訊號，旅行期間有一日我有d野做所以叫屋企人開一開我部電腦，我就用teamviewer控，控完就用teamviwer直接熄埋機。<br />\n主機開關制燈都有著<br />\ncpu,display card風扇都有郁<br />\n試過拆左ram咁開機，平時應該會開唔到機然後一直reboot,但係依加竟然唔會，其他硬件會正常運作<br />\n<br />\n請問下應該點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx"},{"pid":"add9a778748d065f6be1256512e23176010542c2","tid":320141,"uid":93085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:20:38.000Z","msg":"搵人同部電腦傳下心先"},{"pid":"ee254468b3c41cc47df77972514d5bdaf9c933f3","tid":320141,"uid":126697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵人同部電腦傳下心先</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我感覺到你部電腦，而家處於一個好害羞嘅狀態，唔敢見人。<br />\n<br />\n你試下比少少野食氹下佢先"},{"pid":"0cbcbe5740ffbe20dc1a5c1f549c98bbc41f6a16","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:29:26.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822f2467da27a810968e66e754885157600270fd","tid":320141,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:31:31.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會係個mon有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0aa5cd690b70316f66462c869cbc6963abed13e","tid":320141,"uid":67325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實會唔會係個mon有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申:9up"},{"pid":"02606a340b75dd420151e2a10e0ae9ee7496a8a7","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實會唔會係個mon有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n利申:9up</blockquote><br />\n應該唔會<br />\n因為之前當有咁既情況我就會用teamviewer 控我部電腦，如果係開到機但mon有問題既話teamviewer會入到我部機，但今次我用teamviewer入唔到，顯示目標電腦冇開機既情況<br />\n<br />\nbtw thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6968e0f6a40ac05d44d2ca9fb1dc9f03c5ee65ac","tid":320141,"uid":8902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"鬆ram，掃下條槽，再插返實，開機<br />\n<br />\n整完好大機會開得返"},{"pid":"2d0103864d575d7db826385f88c9e6daaeccabc6","tid":320141,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"凶手就係屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef58f1b7cdbb0025faccc7b27be024c58d971046","tid":320141,"uid":15194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:43:47.000Z","msg":"簡單 拆ram 睇下 睇返個底板 本身有冇卡 直接開機<br />\n開到咪就係ram鬆/入塵<br />\n買支掃+刷ram鉛筆頭（白色頭）掃下刷下<br />\n<br />\n咇可能火牛問題都唔定 供電不足"},{"pid":"a33a840ffb2213c0deb1b53c58ecd5ef140e9973","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬆ram，掃下條槽，再插返實，開機<br />\n<br />\n整完好大機會開得返</blockquote><br />\n我試試，唔該你先"},{"pid":"c2d41f29b2170d9e9e91ee23a20157bf1b9d10d2","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡單 拆ram 睇下 睇返個底板 本身有冇卡 直接開機<br />\n開到咪就係ram鬆/入塵<br />\n買支掃+刷ram鉛筆頭（白色頭）掃下刷下<br />\n<br />\n咇可能火牛問題都唔定 供電不足</blockquote><br />\n唔好意思巴打小弟唔係好明咩叫 底板本身有冇卡 <br />\n<br />\n同埋我上面所講既咇一聲係平時開機既聲黎，我係想表達有開機聲(都係唔知點表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )既意思"},{"pid":"05e4aa2f36826e9d472190ce976d4e246c8ef474","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬆ram，掃下條槽，再插返實，開機<br />\n<br />\n整完好大機會開得返</blockquote><br />\n睇落都唔係好多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都照掃左掃，但都係唔得"},{"pid":"1d01b9f2510d1f46d15efb603a8d09410e9374f9","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/190217_afb452bbc53cba6f0f2242f7dfc50885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F190217_afb452bbc53cba6f0f2242f7dfc50885.jpg&h=80135e6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d15df591832f9ebd8f4651da8f0069fe1c133","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:15:14.000Z","msg":"再推推"},{"pid":"0409ebe4451ecbea782c154e60637dab573f713e","tid":320141,"uid":122394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:27:54.000Z","msg":"有無畫面 ？入唔入到bios?"},{"pid":"51db8ab4558b35043f0447a97b9030e13f223f38","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無畫面 ？入唔入到bios?</blockquote><br />\n有平時開機個''咇''一聲，但係冇畫面"},{"pid":"1c9885c60a5acccf1efe9de472f7c85650ef9a2f","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bed5bfca2483ba52dd0d00de2d31801d4c3b650f","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb09ecd92670692bf788b750b21112affa1c4ca","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea072b5cc2ded2763d97a7207a9ac3aaf856c471","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T12:33:01.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打可以救下小弟"},{"pid":"82bd8c89963a534f777b35b94631c03a537e0c6c","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":