s=\"hkgmoji\" />點解要咁做</blockquote><br />\n唔想搞咁多野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋最想知都係究竟係咪真係壞底板，萬一唔係就on99晒左買板既錢又搞唔返掂部機</blockquote><br />\n隔離post又係同我地一樣 但佢擦幾擦ram就着返</blockquote><br />\n我同佢個情況唔同喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔係一直reboot,而係個主機按完開關之後有正常既開機聲，但係個畫面就係冇訊號咁乜都冇，而實際係冇開機既，因為如果有開到但係mon/顯示卡出問題既話用teamviewer會入到"},{"pid":"372196ef0369ddfb0dd5803bb2bd43598b6f6b73","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成部機 拆散 所有野, 淨係 要底板,CPU, 火牛, keyboard or Mon , 再用筆開機 睇下入唔入到BIOS 先</blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加試，係咪hdd ssd都唔插"},{"pid":"303aaeb241be4d0002c84ac409becda8e4a53a6f","tid":320141,"uid":56989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成部機 拆散 所有野, 淨係 要底板,CPU, 火牛, keyboard or Mon , 再用筆開機 睇下入唔入到BIOS 先</blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加試，係咪hdd ssd都唔插</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩遂條ram試 終於着返機 睇黎係壞ram"},{"pid":"5eb3e5c23a7e3ef6a247a35bdcf9f7f6f0de91b1","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成部機 拆散 所有野, 淨係 要底板,CPU, 火牛, keyboard or Mon , 再用筆開機 睇下入唔入到BIOS 先</blockquote><br />\n唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依加試，係咪hdd ssd都唔插</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩遂條ram試 終於着返機 睇黎係壞ram</blockquote><br />\n我都唔知道係咩問題，如果係死ram/冇插/冇插實既話按電源制應該會著幾秒就會熄，然後又再著不停loop，但係依加我部機就係抆埋ram都唔會loop上面個情況，反正好似平常開機咁既樣(實際冇開到)"},{"pid":"38b3b4d37128996debfe40ae2b360ffa0c03991f","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134b8dd8f22b7a1b2b39593d2654acaa22c74a73","tid":320141,"uid":17517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:08:15.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n其實咩叫用筆開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee11cfd24968b30d4436961468d4f3a1efca8933","tid":320141,"uid":25845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推 <br />\n<br />\n其實咩叫用筆開機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用他筆short底板power button果兩個pin"},{"pid":"a7787facc917765744287359f29cff9aaddab3cc","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0933013b974214b01b21355e770a9fead2f797ec","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:31:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b2f83133b9eb03a9cee322dbb639071efea13d0","tid":320141,"uid":118131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"拆剩1 RAM, 拆DISPLAY , 改用內置, 睇下開唔開到機? <br />\n<br />\n開唔到, 請插換另一條RAM再試.<br />\n<br />\n唔得再講"},{"pid":"616ac5e392377c42f5f59954bfe398b7dfacb0c9","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拆剩1 RAM, 拆DISPLAY , 改用內置, 睇下開唔開到機? <br />\n<br />\n開唔到, 請插換另一條RAM再試.<br />\n<br />\n唔得再講</blockquote><br />\n我本身得一條8gb RAM,試左唔得"},{"pid":"7fe6fbf440ae57df21ed4bc7327833df03fd731d","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p