img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cmos電"},{"pid":"29c1060741b5f6393bb14d2ea85b3b06b22184d2","tid":320141,"uid":802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"似ram問題<br />\n問人借條試下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57352bbedafdf07cd7608651c42c3a4aa8243ff0","tid":320141,"uid":21149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n愈睇愈似我個情況<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9966214c96bed16795156fd444a8ef28de637d92","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:23:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cmos電</blockquote><br />\n我都希望係問題係出係cmos電到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 換一換就搞掂"},{"pid":"950382633f2239d4c0d82dbd98efb31d363e6b19","tid":320141,"uid":5166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似ram問題<br />\n問人借條試下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係ram問題唔係會boot唔起，不停boot熄boot熄咁loop緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我部電腦依加個情況係有冇插ram咁開機都會好平時咁既現象(主機有開機個下咇聲，風扇有郁)，但係實際就係冇開到機既，mon亦都冇訊號"},{"pid":"7cb2cf0ea479cca4a278cabedc366136524c93a6","tid":320141,"uid":15009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T16:37:03.000Z","msg":"到我又開唔到機啦求救<br />\n本身一開機著mon但卡死開機黑畫面window標誌個個位<br />\n重開左幾次都唔得，入左window修復個度就keyboard mouse都無電（本身一開機簡正常開機/建議開機有電的）<br />\n拆左ram出黎吹一吹再入返<br />\n依家直接mon都黑埋開機得電流聲<br />\n所有fan都著包括火牛fan<br />\n部機一年半左右<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h